{"word":"G746 - ἀρχή - archḗ - ar-khay' - Beginning","slug":"G746","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀρχή</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>archḗ"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>ar-khay'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Beginning"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03B1;&#x0313;&#x03C1;&#x03C7;&#x03B7;&#x0301; - arche&#x0304;</b> - <i>ar-khay'</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G756\">G756</a>; (properly abstract) a <i>commencement</i>, or (concrete) <i>chief</i> (in various applications of order, time, place or rank): - beginning, corner, (at the, the) first (estate), magistrate, power, principality, principle, rule."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G536\">G536</a>, <a href=\"#/G744\">G744</a>, <a href=\"#/G747\">G747</a>, <a href=\"#/G757\">G757</a>, <a href=\"#/G758\">G758</a>"}]}